related_questions.question: What is a neck wallet?
related_questions.snippet: A neck wallet (also sometimes called a “neck pouch”) is an anti-theft device you can wear underneath your clothing to carry valuable items including your cash, cards, and passports. Never wear anti-theft items on the exterior of your clothing.
